original_title: WCW Clash of The Champions XXXV
overview: "Diamond" Dallas Page & "The Total Package" Lex Luger battle Scott Hall & "Macho Man" Randy Savage. "The Nature Boy" Ric Flair & Curt Hennig take on Konnan & Syxx. Steve "Mongo" McMichael challenges "Double J" Jeff Jarrett for the WCW United States Championship. Ultimo Dragon defends the WCW World Television Championship against "Das Wunderkind" Alex Wright. "Lionheart" Chris Jericho puts up the WCW Cruiserweight Championship against Eddy Guerrero and much more!
title: WCW Clash of The Champions XXXV
